descriptionNullable:
Shrunk the user_anime portion of the dataset for collabrative filtering.

Contains anime_ids and user_ids for four different sizes of the dataset, 'large', 'mid', 'small' and 'tiny' as we go from large to small we quarter the number of users each time, i.e. mid contains a quarter the users of large, small a quarter of mid. 

'large' is basically all the users we can use subject to what I think are minimal and reasonable constraints.

see https://www.kaggle.com/code/luffyd/shrink-user-anime?scriptVersionId=138169383

for details.
